---
import Layout from "../components/layout.astro";
import Title from "../components/ui/title.astro";
import { EMAILS } from "../lib/URL-helpers";
---

<Layout
  title="Epistola · Privacy"
  description="How Epistola handles data when you run the platform or engage with our website."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
      <Title level={1} class="mt-4"> How we handle data </Title>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--muted-text)]">
        Epistola is an open-source renderer. When you self-host it, your organization remains in full control of all
        data. The following details cover how we treat information for our public website, demo environment, and
        optional managed service.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-10 text-[var(--color-peach-paper-copy)]">
        <section>
          <Title level={2}>Website analytics</Title>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We only collect anonymous traffic statistics (page views, referrers, and device types) to understand how
            visitors discover Epistola. We do not use advertising cookies or share analytics data with third parties.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <Title level={2}>Demo environment</Title>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The hosted demo runs sample templates and placeholder data. Documents generated in the demo are
            automatically purged within 24 hours. Do not upload personal or production datasets to the demo instance.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <Title level={2}>Managed service</Title>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you opt for Epistola’s managed offering, a separate Data Processing Agreement (DPA) specifies
            responsibilities, retention, and regional hosting options. We only process the data required to provide the
            service and never reuse it for other purposes.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <Title level={2}>Contact</Title>
          <p class="mt-3">
            For privacy-related questions or DPA requests, email <a
              class="underline hover:text-[var(--color-peach-paper-accent)]"
              href={EMAILS.PRIVACY}>privacy@epistola.app</a
            >.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
